In Amazon VPC, every VPC automatically comes with an implicit virtual router.
This router behaves like a physical router in a data center, but it is fully managed by AWS 

ğŸ”¹ VPC Router & Interfaces
Each subnet inside a VPC has a router interface at:
ğŸ‘‰ The first usable IP address of the subnet (usually x.x.x.1)
Example:
